<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٠٤ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَبِهِ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ الْحَكَمَ عَنْ عَشَرَةِ أَجْرِبَةٍ بِخَمْسَةَ عَشَرَ،<span style="color:#006d98"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَا بَأْسَ بِهِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>